    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/181140897/26b9736a2d14fc4162b2448963f45695_6273573888104950773.png",
                "id": "talent99699",
                "key": "雲來劍法",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雲來劍法"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>，生成手牌<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">雷楔</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/181140897/855f8d96be42fe05d7f7d66b60fad1a6_2935218451651697010.png",
                "id": "talent99825",
                "key": "星斗歸位",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "星斗歸位"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成4點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>，對所有敵方後臺角色造成3點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/181140897/9950bc530ec62d8e01daf47fe1229216_2898008852263531305.png",
                "id": "talent24609",
                "key": "天街巡遊",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "天街巡遊"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">事件牌</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">戰鬥行動</span>：將刻晴切換到場上，立刻使用星斗歸位。本次星斗歸位會爲刻晴附加<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素附魔</span>。但是不會再生成雷楔。</p><p>（刻晴使用星斗歸位時，如果此牌在手中：不會生成雷楔，而是改爲棄置此牌，并爲刻晴附加<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素附魔</span>）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_4332968489610916454.png",
                "id": "talent45713",
                "key": "雷楔",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/d6793b3314d1b255f49f2ba1ec500b38_1324585334713010212.png",
                "title": "雷楔"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本傷害+1，生成「<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span>」</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化領域</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_2229372726493942053.png",
                "id": "talent18241",
                "key": "雷元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">戰鬥行動</span></strong></p><p>我方執行了一次戰鬥行動後，會輪到對方行動。</p><p>打出具有此規則的手牌是一個戰鬥行動，而非快速行動。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雷元素附魔</span></strong></p><p>所附屬角色造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>變爲<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持續回合：2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持續回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合結束階段，持續回合-1；</p><p>持續回合耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></strong></p><p>穿透傷害無法受到傷害加成，但是也無法被護盾、傷害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_2772417273211659357.png",
                "id": "talent51117",
                "key": "規則解釋",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "規則解釋"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
